data.description: Unlock extraordinary savings with a seller offer to receive an enticing 2% of the purchase price towards a buyers' rate buy down. Elevate your home-buying experience and secure exceptional value on your dream property that features 5-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence with a 3-car garage, boasting a grand sweeping entry that sets the tone for the luxurious living within. Why wait on new when you can have an established neighborhood with mature landscaping already in vs waiting years to see trees like these.  The first floor encompasses a versatile den/office, a cozy family room, a convenient powder room, an expansive kitchen with both formal and casual dining areas, a well-appointed laundry room, and the owners' bedroom retreat. The owners' suite is a sanctuary of comfort, featuring a garden tub, a walk-in shower, and a raised vanity with double sinks. The kitchen is a culinary haven, equipped with granite counters, a walk-in pantry, an island, pull-out shelves, and elegant cherry cabinets with 42'' uppers. Premium stainless steel KitchenAid appliances include a 6-burner gas cooktop, built-in microwave/convection oven, and double ovens. The functionality extends to the laundry room, complete with cabinets and a utility sink. The family room and rear patio are thoughtfully wired for sound, enhancing the overall entertainment experience. The second floor offers a versatile loft, a generously sized linen closet, and four bedrooms, three of which boast walk-in closets. The guest bathroom features double sinks for added convenience. The exterior of the home is adorned with mature trees providing ample shade, a meticulous drip/sprinkler system, spacious patio, and a concrete pad with a 220-volt power supply, perfect for installing a spa or setting up an amazing outdoor kitchen. The interior received a thoughtful update in 2018, including fresh paint, updated lighting, new carpet, additional cabinetry, and upgraded kitchen appliances. Further enhancements in 2019 introduced stylish wood laminate flooring. Appreciation for your visit to this meticulously maintained residence.
